WEBVTT

00:00:18.895 --> 00:00:20.340
⟨EST' O CHЁМ⟩?

00:00:21.426 --> 00:00:22.517
DA?

00:00:23.306 --> 00:00:26.344
vu hot ir gelebt in Shantser lager?

00:00:29.003 --> 00:00:32.827
Shantser lager? ⟨s'iz shoyn⟩ geven a oysgestroyeter lager,

00:00:36.057 --> 00:00:38.801
un a, un mit barakes.

00:00:39.668 --> 00:00:44.151
nu, un ale hobn gelebt; s'iz geven di ershter, tsveyter, driter barak.

00:00:45.078 --> 00:00:48.052
men hot gelebt mishpokhevayz?

00:00:49.928 --> 00:00:51.997
di froyen hobn gelebt

00:00:52.594 --> 00:00:57.043
bazunder in a lager, di mener bazunder in a lager.

00:00:57.555 --> 00:00:59.236
dos heyst, in a,

00:01:00.002 --> 00:01:02.088
in a barak, nu.

00:01:02.719 --> 00:01:03.646
VOT TAK.

00:01:03.701 --> 00:01:05.954
vu iz geven ayer meydele?

00:01:06.364 --> 00:01:08.821
zi iz geven mit mir tsuzamen.

00:01:11.177 --> 00:01:15.156
vos hot zi gegesn? mit vos hot ir gekent ir kormenen?

00:01:18.177 --> 00:01:22.929
vos men, vos in lager flegt men oyskokhn. s'iz geven a kikh.

00:01:23.982 --> 00:01:29.578
vos m'hot gekokht in lager un m'hot gegebn esn, dos hobn ale gegesn:

00:01:29.584 --> 00:01:31.597
di groyse, di kleyne,

00:01:31.597 --> 00:01:33.223
ale, di zelbe.

00:01:35.083 --> 00:01:38.046
ir hot zikh gekent zen mit ayer man?

00:01:38.410 --> 00:01:39.399
DA.

00:01:40.603 --> 00:01:41.879
ale tog.

00:01:43.497 --> 00:01:45.694
vu hot gearbet ayer man?

00:01:47.286 --> 00:01:49.338
er iz geven a SANTEKHNIK.

00:01:50.695 --> 00:01:56.935
nu, er hot gearbet in shtot. ikh veys nit vu UNK dortn... a! in di klinikes hobn zey gearbet.

00:01:56.935 --> 00:02:00.870
ale SANTEKHNIKs hobn gearbet in di klinikes.

00:02:01.005 --> 00:02:01.775
DA.

00:02:03.267 --> 00:02:04.965
m'hot gestroyet

00:02:05.629 --> 00:02:07.125
klinikes,

00:02:07.755 --> 00:02:12.046
hot men gestroyet. un dortn hobn gearbet ale SANTEKHNIKs.

00:02:12.700 --> 00:02:14.702
er hot dortn oykh gearbet.

00:02:16.625 --> 00:02:22.722
az er iz geven in shtot, hot er zikh gekent zen mit, ⟨n-⟩ nit mit yidishe, mit andere mentshn?

00:02:25.221 --> 00:02:26.801
ikh halt az neyn.

00:02:27.887 --> 00:02:29.335
bay der arbet...

00:02:29.335 --> 00:02:30.969
zey flegn dokh firn

00:02:31.482 --> 00:02:35.267
bay der arbet un fun der arbet brengen tsurik

00:02:35.267 --> 00:02:36.372
in geto.

00:02:36.372 --> 00:02:38.765
flegt men darfn durkhgeyn dem toyer.

00:02:39.042 --> 00:02:39.846
DA.

00:02:40.375 --> 00:02:42.231
iz ergets hot men nit gekent...

00:02:42.231 --> 00:02:44.616
nu, s'iz geven azelkhene

00:02:44.616 --> 00:02:47.912
vos flegn take avekgeyn in shtiblekh

00:02:48.475 --> 00:02:50.106
oysbaytn.

00:02:50.432 --> 00:02:53.143
nu, in geto, ver s'hot gehat

00:02:53.419 --> 00:02:57.238
a iberike kofte, a iberike por shikh, veys vos,

00:02:57.238 --> 00:02:59.504
un m'hot gedarft hobn tsum esn,

00:02:59.545 --> 00:03:01.513
flegt men dos in shtot

00:03:01.570 --> 00:03:03.133
avektrogn

00:03:03.156 --> 00:03:05.310
oysbaytn oyf broyt.

00:03:05.907 --> 00:03:09.934
ikh hob gehat a ney-mashin, a naye, a SINGER.

00:03:09.973 --> 00:03:12.431
ober oyb⟨e⟩ ikh hob gedarft hobn

00:03:13.905 --> 00:03:15.114
broyt,

00:03:15.373 --> 00:03:18.236
hob ikh mayn mashin opgegebn.

00:03:19.558 --> 00:03:21.560
far a shtikl broyt

00:03:22.528 --> 00:03:26.060
mit a kilo SALe hob ikh avekgegebn di mashin,

00:03:26.060 --> 00:03:26.946
vos kh'hob,

00:03:26.946 --> 00:03:29.323
a naye mashin, a SINGER⟨'s⟩.

00:03:29.616 --> 00:03:33.120
UNK a por yor biz kh'hob oysgetsolt im,

00:03:33.852 --> 00:03:36.208
vayl er iz, er hot gekost nit bilik.

00:03:36.450 --> 00:03:39.684
nu, kh'hob avekgegebn vayl ikh hob gedarft hobn broyt.

00:03:41.185 --> 00:03:43.157
vemen hot ir avekgegebn?

00:03:43.166 --> 00:03:45.034
 vi meynt ir vemen?

00:03:45.394 --> 00:03:46.687
di lamedn.

00:03:46.930 --> 00:03:48.561
arayn a lamed,

00:03:50.629 --> 00:03:51.513
DA,

00:03:52.667 --> 00:03:55.305
un er hot gebrakht broyt

00:03:55.502 --> 00:03:59.925
mit SALe, un er hot tsugenumen di mashin un er iz avek.

00:04:01.847 --> 00:04:04.186
vemen ken men dos avekgebn?

00:04:10.909 --> 00:04:12.084
VOT TAK.

00:04:15.983 --> 00:04:19.000
vu hot ir gearbet in ŠANČIAI lager?

00:04:20.476 --> 00:04:23.441
oykhet in, i⟨n m-⟩ in,

00:04:23.903 --> 00:04:26.630
in a man- masterskaye, a shnayderay.

00:04:28.833 --> 00:04:31.205
vos hot ir dortn ge⟨SH-⟩...

00:04:30.897 --> 00:04:32.064
geneyt?

00:04:31.564 --> 00:04:32.897
geneyt, ye.

00:04:33.555 --> 00:04:36.468
oykh far di daytshn. zey flegn brengen

00:04:36.593 --> 00:04:39.096
latns tserisene,

00:04:39.096 --> 00:04:42.105
un me fleg zey darfn far-, -latenen:

00:04:44.811 --> 00:04:46.706
tsuzamenshtepn,

00:04:46.706 --> 00:04:48.939
a late leygn, un dos.

00:04:49.013 --> 00:04:51.538
oder zey flegn, brengen

00:04:52.354 --> 00:04:57.478
dortn, kh'veys nit, dortn hoyzn oder vos, far di daytshn.

00:04:57.889 --> 00:04:59.536
far zey hot men geneyt.

00:05:01.185 --> 00:05:03.910
m'hot aykh getsolt far di arbet?

00:05:03.025 --> 00:05:07.276
ney-. neyn!

00:05:07.808 --> 00:05:09.256
ver tsolt dos?

00:05:16.382 --> 00:05:18.707
ir hot gehat zakhn far zikh?

00:05:19.175 --> 00:05:21.345
vos hot ir getrogn vinter?

00:05:23.691 --> 00:05:28.781
ikh gedenk shoyn gornit. vos ikh hob gehat, di zelbe zakhn, dos hob ikh getrogn.

00:05:36.752 --> 00:05:40.104
az m- az m'hot undz gebrakht in Shtuthof,

00:05:40.549 --> 00:05:43.158
hot men alemen geheysn

00:05:43.283 --> 00:05:47.406
zikh oyston di zakhn. m'hot gefirt in bod: "oyston di zakhn."

00:05:47.406 --> 00:05:49.419
zey hobn gedarft dos durkhkukn.

00:05:49.678 --> 00:05:52.304
un nokh dem hot men mir gegebn

00:05:52.480 --> 00:05:54.448
gor a vayse kleydele.

00:05:55.028 --> 00:05:58.721
a vayse kleydl, hert! vinter. s'iz kalt,

00:05:59.888 --> 00:06:01.822
un me darf geyn arbetn.

00:06:02.183 --> 00:06:06.577
a vayse kleydele, a zumerdike, mit a kurtsn arbl.

00:06:06.577 --> 00:06:09.649
un mayne zakhn, di vareme, hot men tsugenumen,

00:06:09.649 --> 00:06:11.323
avekgegebn a andern.

00:06:13.352 --> 00:06:15.472
I vos hot ir geton

00:06:15.472 --> 00:06:17.319
⟨in d- azane⟩ badingungen?

00:06:17.134 --> 00:06:21.903
⟨nu⟩, vos hob ikh gezolt ton? vos ikh ho- vos m'hot mir gegebn, dos hob ikh getrogn.

00:06:22.112 --> 00:06:24.738
vu hob ikh gekent nemen andere zakhn?

00:06:26.787 --> 00:06:28.671
mayne hot men tsugenumen,

00:06:28.997 --> 00:06:30.611
avekgegebn a andern.

00:06:34.628 --> 00:06:39.113
bay aykh iz nit gevorn ⟨opgefrire⟩t di, di hent, di fis?

00:06:40.084 --> 00:06:40.938
neyn.

00:06:42.903 --> 00:06:45.402
vos hot ir getrogn oyf di fis?

00:06:49.216 --> 00:06:50.608
oyf di fis...

00:06:52.352 --> 00:06:57.881
ikh gedenk, ikh hob nit gehat vos tsum trogn, take, oyf di fis.

00:06:58.528 --> 00:07:02.605
nor m'hot mir gegebn, ir veyst vos? a por soldatske

00:07:02.646 --> 00:07:03.821
shikh.

00:07:06.443 --> 00:07:08.225
ot dos hob ikh getrogn.

00:07:08.620 --> 00:07:11.021
un az mir zaynen bafrayt gevorn,

00:07:11.021 --> 00:07:12.502
di krig hot zikh geendikt,

00:07:12.502 --> 00:07:16.781
bin ikh mit di soldatske shikh gekumen in Lite.

00:07:16.804 --> 00:07:19.746
un ⟨kh'⟩fleg geyn bay der arbet in masterska⟨y⟩,

00:07:19.746 --> 00:07:24.783
vu ale flegn shoyn geyn in LODOCHKes un tufelekh ongeton, fayn.

00:07:24.783 --> 00:07:28.056
fleg ikh kumen mit di soldatske shikh:

00:07:28.056 --> 00:07:30.381
top, top, top, top.

00:07:31.975 --> 00:07:36.958
kh'hob zikh nit gekent koyfn a por shikh. s'iz avek a tsayt biz kh'hob zikh ongeklibn

00:07:36.958 --> 00:07:39.092
oyf a por tufelekh.

00:07:42.859 --> 00:07:44.760
ot aza lebn iz geven.

00:07:46.150 --> 00:07:48.186
fun di kindershe yorn

00:07:49.255 --> 00:07:50.363
biz,

00:07:51.162 --> 00:07:53.569
biz di krig un nokh di krig.

00:07:59.278 --> 00:08:00.639
shverer.

00:08:00.763 --> 00:08:02.562
a shverer lebn geven.

00:08:04.266 --> 00:08:07.154
ver hot aykh bafrayt fun SHTUTTGOF?

00:08:08.205 --> 00:08:10.784
fun Shtuthof hot men dokh undz avekgeshikt

00:08:10.784 --> 00:08:12.317
oyf der arbet.

00:08:13.521 --> 00:08:17.083
di rusn zaynen arayn un mir zaynen bafrayt gevorn.

00:08:17.335 --> 00:08:21.246
az mir z- az mir z- undz hot men avekgefirt

00:08:21.246 --> 00:08:22.745
in a vald,

00:08:24.355 --> 00:08:28.601
un dortn hobn undz di daytshn ibergelozn. un zey hobn gezogt,

00:08:28.827 --> 00:08:31.031
"mir muzn avek.

00:08:31.898 --> 00:08:34.676
aykh, froyen, vet shoyn gut zayn.

00:08:35.610 --> 00:08:38.067
undz, keyn mol nit."

00:08:38.918 --> 00:08:40.414
azoy hobn zey gezogt.

00:08:42.917 --> 00:08:45.509
zey lebn gornit shlekht in Daytshland.

00:08:47.440 --> 00:08:49.526
es darf nor pasirn

00:08:49.836 --> 00:08:53.081
az d⟨i⟩ erd zol zikh fanandershpaltn

00:08:53.081 --> 00:08:55.432
un zey alemen araynshlingen,

00:08:55.708 --> 00:08:56.962
ale daytshn,

00:08:56.962 --> 00:09:01.372
mit di kinder, mit di froyen, mit di alte, alemen tsuzamen.

00:09:01.378 --> 00:09:03.464
ot dos darf pasirn.

00:09:04.483 --> 00:09:06.353
un dos vet pasirn.

00:09:06.353 --> 00:09:08.700
ir veyst vos? ikh hob geleyent:

00:09:08.700 --> 00:09:10.452
az me hot getribn,

00:09:10.592 --> 00:09:13.623
aroysgetribn di yidn fun Mitsraim,

00:09:15.925 --> 00:09:17.036
di Araber,

00:09:18.372 --> 00:09:21.043
hobn zey getribn tsum yam.

00:09:21.386 --> 00:09:23.512
zey hobn gevelt dertrinken ale yidn.

00:09:23.755 --> 00:09:26.089
un az di yidn zaynen tsu bayn yam,

00:09:26.089 --> 00:09:27.810
hot zikh der yam ts-

00:09:27.810 --> 00:09:30.870
fanandergeshpoltn. ir hot dos ven geleyent?

00:09:30.673 --> 00:09:31.494
ye.

00:09:31.399 --> 00:09:34.883
un s'iz gevorn a SUKHAYA DOROZHKA,

00:09:34.883 --> 00:09:37.058
un ale yidn zaynen durkh,

00:09:37.058 --> 00:09:39.883
un hinter zey zaynen gegangen di Araber.

00:09:39.883 --> 00:09:43.868
hot zikh der vaser tsuzamengegosn un di Araber zaynen dertrunken.

00:09:44.376 --> 00:09:47.857
trakht ikh az s'iz do oyf der velt nisim.

00:09:47.857 --> 00:09:50.292
 un ikh bet bay got

00:09:50.552 --> 00:09:53.890
az er zol tsuhern mayn gebet,

00:09:53.910 --> 00:09:55.485
un di erd

00:09:55.485 --> 00:09:58.157
in Daytshland zol zikh shpaltn,

00:09:58.365 --> 00:10:01.025
un ale daytshn araynshlingen.

00:10:01.099 --> 00:10:04.459
ot dos bet ikh, un ikh volt dos nokh gevelt derlebn.

00:10:04.575 --> 00:10:06.943
ikh hof az dos vet azoy zayn.

00:10:06.943 --> 00:10:12.208
oybe der yam hot zikh gekent shpaltn un di vaser zikh fananderteyln,

00:10:12.208 --> 00:10:14.846
iz vos ken zikh di erd nit shpaltn?

00:10:15.898 --> 00:10:17.839
zi muz zikh shpaltn,

00:10:18.058 --> 00:10:20.802
un araynshlingen zey alemen:

00:10:20.927 --> 00:10:23.717
di daytshn, ⟨m-⟩ mit di kinder,

00:10:23.717 --> 00:10:27.165
mit di eltern zeyere, mit alemen tsuzamen.

00:10:28.578 --> 00:10:34.277
ir hot gekrogn hilf fun di sovyetishe armey ven aykh hot men bafrayt?

00:10:34.444 --> 00:10:36.480
vos hob ikh gekent krign?

00:10:37.802 --> 00:10:40.347
keyn zakhn hobn ni- undz nit gegebn.

00:10:41.515 --> 00:10:44.664
DAZHE keyn RATSION. m'hot gezogt,

00:10:45.632 --> 00:10:48.444
"ot do, az ir't kumen oyf di

00:10:50.070 --> 00:10:54.148
OSTANOVKe, vet men aykh aroysgebn produktn."

00:10:55.251 --> 00:11:00.049
az mir zaynen gekumen ot do, hot men undz gezogt az "dortn,

00:11:00.049 --> 00:11:02.620
ir't kumen, vet men aykh dortn gebn."

00:11:02.620 --> 00:11:08.423
dortn, dortn, dortn; mir zaynen gekumen aheym un ⟨ot⟩ UNK ⟨dos nit gegebn⟩.

00:11:08.423 --> 00:11:10.112
keyn zakhn undz nit gegebn!

00:11:11.704 --> 00:11:14.060
s'iz nito keyn emes bay ⟨z-⟩.

00:11:14.496 --> 00:11:20.846
⟨un⟩ ven hot ir gekumen in Lite? vi iz geven di veg fun Daytshland biz Lite?

00:11:20.824 --> 00:11:21.605
⟨i-⟩...

00:11:20.948 --> 00:11:24.788
vifl tsayt hot ir farbrakht in veg?

00:11:22.686 --> 00:11:26.729
in Lite? dos iz shoyn geven in, in zeks un fertsikstn yor.

00:11:28.583 --> 00:11:33.197
bizn zeks un, zeks un fertsikstn yor, vu zayt ir geven?

00:11:33.304 --> 00:11:36.718
nu, do⟨s, in, dos⟩ zaynen mir geven bay der arbet.

00:11:36.718 --> 00:11:40.486
az mir zaynen shoyn bafrayt gevorn, iz in Poyln

00:11:41.117 --> 00:11:43.136
hot men undz geheysn

00:11:43.446 --> 00:11:46.016
arbetn. vos arbetn?

00:11:46.016 --> 00:11:47.476
far di polyakn,

00:11:47.476 --> 00:11:51.695
in di k⟨e-⟩ podvaln, iberklaybn zeyere bulves:

00:11:51.695 --> 00:11:55.719
velkhe s'iz farfoylte leygn on a zayt, un di gute on a zayt.

00:11:55.719 --> 00:11:58.239
hot men dos undz gegebn di arbet.

00:11:59.275 --> 00:12:00.596
 nakher,

00:12:00.596 --> 00:12:02.559
vos hot men nokh geheysn?

00:12:02.869 --> 00:12:03.656
nu,

00:12:04.489 --> 00:12:09.258
azelkhene kleynikeyt. dos hobn di polyakn gebetn, me zol zey helfn.

00:12:10.463 --> 00:12:13.731
nu, VSЁ. nakher, ⟨⟩, zaynen mir geforn oyf,

00:12:13.804 --> 00:12:15.992
oyfn poyezd.

00:12:21.516 --> 00:12:25.492
nu, nit keyn normaler poyezd, nor, ⟨⟩, ikh veys nit

00:12:26.427 --> 00:12:28.463
voser a poyezd dortn geven.

00:12:31.472 --> 00:12:36.630
dortn iz geven ongegruzet, un mir hobn gedarft lign fun oybn.

00:12:37.378 --> 00:12:40.457
TOVARNer, TOVARNer poyezd.

00:12:41.361 --> 00:12:43.464
hot men undz opgeshikt aheym.

00:12:44.028 --> 00:12:46.747
 nor vu iz geven mayn kop?

00:12:46.947 --> 00:12:50.316
vu ho⟨g⟩ ikh, vu hob ikh gehat a heym?

00:12:50.541 --> 00:12:52.813
un tsu vos bin ikh geforn aheym?

00:12:54.017 --> 00:12:56.272
ikh hob dokh shoyn keyn heym nit gehat.

00:12:58.641 --> 00:13:02.084
s'iz do a lid: "mayn heym hot men tseshtert,

00:13:02.084 --> 00:13:04.895
un mayn heym hot men farvert,

00:13:05.442 --> 00:13:08.205
vayl mir iz azoy bashert."

00:13:08.205 --> 00:13:11.280
vu bin ikh geforn? vu iz geven mayn kop?

00:13:11.280 --> 00:13:14.143
fun Poyln hob ikh dokh gekent avekforn

00:13:14.183 --> 00:13:16.607
tsu mayn mame's shvester.

00:13:20.578 --> 00:13:22.580
⟨iz⟩ di kop nit gearbet.

00:13:23.380 --> 00:13:25.011
nit gearbet di kop.

00:13:25.472 --> 00:13:29.934
vifl felern ikh hob geton in mayn lebn, ken ikh aykh nit zogn.

00:13:31.142 --> 00:13:34.629
un ikh bin, dakht zikh, gornit aza DUROCHKe.

00:13:35.175 --> 00:13:37.801
un VECHNe hob ikh gemakht felern.

00:13:37.926 --> 00:13:38.679
nu...

00:13:40.103 --> 00:13:42.729
tsu forn ⟨i-⟩ in Lite.

00:13:43.393 --> 00:13:44.484
"aheym."

00:13:45.773 --> 00:13:47.285
vu iz mayn heym?

00:13:48.405 --> 00:13:51.419
nit keyn shtub, nit keyn dakh,

00:13:53.029 --> 00:13:55.773
NICHEGO. nokh vos bin ikh do gekumen?

00:13:58.834 --> 00:14:01.528
vos tsores kh'hob do gehat az ikh bin gekumen,

00:14:02.007 --> 00:14:03.722
vos trern!

00:14:06.073 --> 00:14:09.887
nit geven keyn seykhl, un VSЁ. nit geven keyn seykhl.

00:14:16.992 --> 00:14:20.293
me zogt a glaykhvort: vos a mentsh ken zikh ton,

00:14:20.502 --> 00:14:22.824
ken nit der grester soyne.

00:14:23.320 --> 00:14:25.642
s'iz zeyer a rikhtiker vort.

00:14:25.767 --> 00:14:27.414
zeyer a rikhtiker vort.

00:14:28.382 --> 00:14:31.616
vos ikh hob zikh opgeton az ikh bin gekumen ot o do...

00:14:31.875 --> 00:14:33.776
hob keynem nit getrofn.

00:14:34.440 --> 00:14:36.577
elnt azoy vi a shteyn.

00:14:39.638 --> 00:14:44.899
s'iz gut az di vos mi- ikh bin geven mit ir, tsuzamen in lager un umetum,

00:14:44.899 --> 00:14:47.309
hot zi getrofn ir bruder.

00:14:47.687 --> 00:14:50.414
hot zi shoyn gehat vu tsu shlofn,

00:14:50.573 --> 00:14:53.163
un mir hot zi genumen mit zikh,

00:14:53.163 --> 00:14:56.118
vayl mir hobn zikh gehaltn tsuzamen umetum.

00:14:56.665 --> 00:14:59.376
hob ikh shoyn gehat oykh vu ibershlofn.

00:15:00.124 --> 00:15:03.189
un ven i- ven zi treft nit dem bruder,

00:15:03.550 --> 00:15:06.126
voltn mir beyde nit gehat vu tsu shlofn.

00:15:06.790 --> 00:15:10.510
⟨nu, ot⟩ eyne a, eyne, undzere a shokhnte

00:15:10.907 --> 00:15:12.455
fun far di krig...

00:15:13.287 --> 00:15:15.981
mir hobn ir getrofn. zogt zi,

00:15:16.543 --> 00:15:20.261
"kumt bay mir ibershlofn." zi lebt in a keler.

00:15:20.261 --> 00:15:23.408
"nor," zogt zi, "keyn divan hob ikh nit,

00:15:23.408 --> 00:15:26.580
un keyn PODUSHKe un keyn ODEYALe oykh nit,

00:15:26.580 --> 00:15:28.808
⟨un⟩ oyf dr'erd darf men shlofn."

00:15:28.808 --> 00:15:30.324
zogn mir, "gut.

00:15:30.533 --> 00:15:34.189
beser bay aykh oyf dr'erd, eyder bay an andern oyf a divan."

00:15:34.414 --> 00:15:35.963
mir hobn nit gehat avu,

00:15:35.963 --> 00:15:38.171
hobn mir geshlofn bay ir oyf dr'erd.

00:15:39.257 --> 00:15:42.153
on keyn zakh: oyfn ⟨a-⟩ oyfn pol.

00:15:43.425 --> 00:15:45.005
nu, vos ken men ton?

00:15:47.458 --> 00:15:50.371
⟨nokh a ne- a⟩, hob ikh getrofn a khaverte.

00:15:51.475 --> 00:15:55.741
zogt zi oykh, "vu shlofstu? vu binstu?" zog ikh, "ikh hob nit avu."

00:15:55.741 --> 00:15:59.301
zogt zi, "nu, oybe du vilst, ot do bay undz in dem tsimer..." a,

00:15:59.301 --> 00:16:01.360
a durkhgangs-tsimer,

00:16:01.360 --> 00:16:03.264
vos me geyt aher, ahin.

00:16:03.264 --> 00:16:08.339
zogt zi, "vayl do in tsimer," zogt zi, "iz ale fraynd, vifl mir zaynen lebn geblibn,

00:16:08.339 --> 00:16:09.983
shlofn mir ale tsuzamen."

00:16:09.983 --> 00:16:13.735
zogt zi, "oybe du vilst ot do oyfn divan," in durkhgangs-tsimer...

00:16:13.735 --> 00:16:15.701
zog ikh, "gut, zol zayn do."

00:16:15.825 --> 00:16:20.311
I vifl shmates ver s'hot gehat, hot men oyf mir aro⟨yf⟩gevorfn;

00:16:20.311 --> 00:16:23.295
s'iz geven vinter, ikh zol nit farfrorn vern.

00:16:30.068 --> 00:16:32.492
me ken dos shoyn keyn film nit zen,

00:16:33.072 --> 00:16:35.563
dos vos ikh hob durkhgemakht in mayn lebn.

00:16:37.649 --> 00:16:40.528
vi hot ir zikh dernokh ayngeordnt?

00:16:41.357 --> 00:16:43.393
vi hob ikh zikh ayngeordnt?

00:16:44.428 --> 00:16:46.261
mayne a khaverte

00:16:46.500 --> 00:16:49.096
hot mir gezogt... zi hot gekent

00:16:49.440 --> 00:16:52.137
dem zelbn bokher vos ikh,

00:16:52.137 --> 00:16:54.000
vos kh'hob khasene gehat mit im.

00:16:54.000 --> 00:16:57.601
zogt zi, "du veyst vos ikh'l dir zogn? mayn meynung iz,

00:16:57.912 --> 00:16:59.627
er iz a shtiler

00:16:59.818 --> 00:17:01.043
mentsh,

00:17:01.043 --> 00:17:03.424
un du host gedarft mit im khasene hobn.

00:17:03.424 --> 00:17:07.897
un fun der arbet git men zey dires, vestu glaykh hobn a dire.

00:17:07.897 --> 00:17:09.904
⟨du vest⟩ glaykh zayn a baleboste."

00:17:10.602 --> 00:17:12.266
"nu," trakht ikh,

00:17:13.588 --> 00:17:15.236
"ikh hob a breyre?

00:17:15.478 --> 00:17:16.940
azoy vel ikh ton."

00:17:17.082 --> 00:17:19.150
hobn mir beyde khasene gehat,

00:17:19.719 --> 00:17:21.496
un er hot gekrogn a dire.

00:17:22.801 --> 00:17:24.297
nu,

00:17:24.540 --> 00:17:26.626
un azoy hobn mir zikh gelebt.

00:17:29.299 --> 00:17:32.263
mit tsvelf yor tsurik iz er geshtorbn.

00:17:32.263 --> 00:17:33.967
er hot gehat a YAZVe.

00:17:35.914 --> 00:17:42.708
nu, iz er avekgeshtorbn. azoy hobn mir gelebt tsuzamen di gantse tsayt. di kinder geborn: Miren un Doren.

00:17:44.757 --> 00:17:46.776
un take zeyer gut.

00:17:46.933 --> 00:17:50.909
ot hob ikh oyf der elter kinder; anit volt ikh geven eyne.

00:17:53.818 --> 00:17:56.301
eyne. ver volt oyf mir gekukt?

00:17:56.451 --> 00:18:00.073
un ver volt mir geholfn mit vos? un azoy di kinder,

00:18:01.834 --> 00:18:04.308
zey hitn mir vi a kleynem kind.

00:18:04.872 --> 00:18:05.608
DA.

00:18:06.053 --> 00:18:08.797
keyn eyn-hore, keyn eyn-hore! azelkhe kinder

00:18:09.597 --> 00:18:11.312
zet men nit,

00:18:11.571 --> 00:18:13.624
azelkhe gute kinder.

00:18:17.095 --> 00:18:20.353
vos vilt ir zogn di kumendike dorim?

00:18:22.557 --> 00:18:23.684
vos zo-...?

00:18:23.147 --> 00:18:26.463
di tsukunft dorim, di tsukunft kinder.

00:18:26.191 --> 00:18:27.728
in der tsukunft?

00:18:27.284 --> 00:18:28.284
ye.

00:18:28.395 --> 00:18:30.535
in der tsukunft vil ikh,

00:18:31.142 --> 00:18:32.810
zol zayn sholem,

00:18:33.238 --> 00:18:35.847
un ale yidn zol zayn gut,

00:18:35.888 --> 00:18:39.409
vayle tsores hobn ale gehat; se klekt.

00:18:40.258 --> 00:18:45.534
ikh vil, ikh bet ⟨g-⟩ ale tog bay got az s'zol nor zayn sholem.

00:18:46.941 --> 00:18:50.192
sholem bay undz in di yidishe land,

00:18:50.856 --> 00:18:56.115
un sholem oyf der gantser velt. alemen zol zayn gut, un undz oykh.

00:18:57.032 --> 00:18:58.899
ot dos iz mayn

00:18:59.310 --> 00:19:01.481
farlang. ot dos vil ikh.

00:19:01.858 --> 00:19:04.619
ale tog trakht ikh nor vegn sholem.

00:19:05.368 --> 00:19:07.331
oder az ikh shrayb a briv,

00:19:07.331 --> 00:19:09.550
iz dray mol dermont:

00:19:09.550 --> 00:19:13.445
"sholem, fridn, nor fun derayn."

00:19:14.110 --> 00:19:15.538
nor fun derayn.

00:19:15.698 --> 00:19:16.365
DA.

00:19:17.600 --> 00:19:18.669
a dank.

00:19:20.639 --> 00:19:21.950
UNK

00:19:21.372 --> 00:19:22.372
oy.

00:19:32.952 --> 00:19:36.110
