00:20:29.288 --> 00:20:32.961
 dos iz nokh fun di gute yorn, fun far di krig.

00:20:33.512 --> 00:20:35.375
in velkhe shtot?

00:20:36.510 --> 00:20:38.141
⟨shoyn⟩ in Kovne.

00:20:38.961 --> 00:20:39.676
UNK

00:20:42.239 --> 00:20:46.338
